# textdomain: mcl_mud
Mud=Blato
Mud is a decorative block that generates in mangrove swamps. Mud can also be obtained by using water bottles on dirt or coarse dirt.=Blato je okrasni blok, ki nastane v mangrovovih močvirjih. Blato lahko pridobite tudi z uporabo steklenic z vodo na prsti ali grobi prsti.
Packed Mud=Zbito blato
Packed mud is a decorative block used to craft mud bricks.=Zbito blato je okrasni blok, ki se uporablja za izdelavo blatnih opek.
Mud Bricks=Blatna opeka
Decorative block crafted from packed mud.=Okrasni blok, izdelan iz zbitega blata.